  <brief_title>Phase III Randomized Trial of Adjuvant Chemotherapy With S-1 vs S-1/Oxaliplatin ± Radiotherapy for Completely Resected Gastric Adenocarcinoma : The ARTIST II Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>ARTIST-II</acronym>
