  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The optimal regimen for adjuvant treatment has not been established in GC yet. We plan to
      compare TS-1, TS-1/oxaliplatin with or without RT in D2 resected gastric cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
